448
00:37:00.250 --> 00:37:02.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ahora controlo mi vida.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:37:05.291 --> 00:37:06.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cada bocado.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:37:31.666 --> 00:37:34.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
