512
00:41:58.041 --> 00:41:59.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Dijo cuándo?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:41:59.708 --> 00:42:03.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>La asamblea de los nobles.</c.bg_transparent>
