514
00:42:06.083 --> 00:42:07.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gracias.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:42:07.125 --> 00:42:09.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puede que nos hayas salvado a todos,</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:42:09.333 --> 00:42:10.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
